> 
> Flying sentient; now imperial citizens.  See JTAS 15 Contact!
> 
> 
> Akumgeda                Ksinanirz Sector
> (Vargr minor)
> 
> Geneered by Ancients for weird psionic powers.   See "Vilani & Vargr."
> 
> 
> Ahetowa                 (unnamed) / Ealiyasiyw 2604
> 
> Sentience psionic plants (near plants).  Contacted  by Aslan.  See
> Challenge 56 Contact!
> 
> 
> Bolth                   Fulani L (Zachrisson)
> 
> Serpentine race living in Zachrisson subsector,  but though to originate in
> another Galaxy. See  "Vanguard Reaches."
