    'body' => 'I developed a short spreadsheet this evening to help "flesh" out my
worlds as my players explore them. It\'s detailed data on worlds, randomly
generated from the base UPP of Size, Atmo, & Hydro. I took the ranges
from TNE rules and applied them (uniform distributions) to get:
Actual Size
Pressure in ATMs
Hydrographics %
Gravities
Density
Horizon (formula stolen from old striker)

I stuck it all into an Excel spreadsheet, if anyone\'s interested. I uploaded
it to the FTP site at ghost.cc.missouri.edu /PUB/Traveller/TNE/Planet.XLS.

There\'s also a version for Lotus: Planet.WK1 and Planet.FMT
