       to \'protect\' their \'legal rights\' at the expense of their
       market share.

*********************************************************************

Coming Soon:  "Why you can sue the manufacturer of you TL-12 assault
               rifle if it jams in combat, assuming, of course, that
               you survive."

*********************************************************************

David Reed (556N@delphi.com)
